{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"Yã game huska* kuma ya jũya bãya.","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Wani makãho, Abdullahi bin Ummi Maktũm ya je wurin Annabi dõmin ya musulunta, sai ya iske a lõkacin nan Annabi na ƙõƙarin shiryar da wasu manyan mutãne na Ƙuraishãwa, sai wannan makãhon ya yanke maganar Annabi da su, bã da saninsa ba, alhãli Annabi na bũrin su musulunta dõmin darajarsu ga idon mutãnensu. Saboda haka Annabi, (tsira da amincin Allah su tabbata a gare shi), ya ɓata Fuska, ya tafi dõmin ɓacin ransa, saboda rashin musuluntarsu. Bãyan haka Annabi nã girmama Abdullahi ƙwarai, idan ya je wurinsa sai ya ce masa \"Maraba da wanda Ubangijina Ya zarge ni sabõda shi.\" Kuma ya shimfiɗa masa mayafinsa, idan ya fita tafiya, yakan sanya shi riƙon garin Madina, ƙissar tana nũna girmamawar Allah ga Annabi da Ya ce: \"Ya game Fuska.\" Bai ce masa: \"Domin ka game Fuska\" ba, sai ya faɗa a cikin hali mai sauƙi.\".","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:2","price":"Sabõda makãho yã je masa.","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:3","price":"To, me ya sanar da kai cẽwa watakila shi ne zai tsarkaka.","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:4","price":"Ko ya tuna, dõmin tunãwar ta amfane shi?","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:5","price":"Amma wanda ya wadãtu da dũkiya.","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:6","price":"Sa'an nan kai kuma ka ɗora bijira zuwa gare shi!","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:7","price":"To, me zai cũce ka idan bai tsarkaka ba?","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:8","price":"Kuma, amma wanda ya zomaka yana gaugãwa.","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:9","price":"Alhãli shĩ yanã jin tsõrõn Allah.","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:10","price":"Kai kuma kã shagala ga barinsa!","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:11","price":"A'aha! Lalle ne, wannan tunãtarwa ce.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:12","price":"Sabõda wanda ya so ya tuna Shi (Allah).","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:13","price":"(Tunãtarwa ce) ta cikin littafai abãban girmamãwa,","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:14","price":"Abãban ɗaukakãwa, abãban tsarkakẽwa.","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:15","price":"A cikin hannãyen mala'iku marubũta.","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:16","price":"Mãsu daraja, mãsu ɗã'a ga Allah.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:17","price":"An la'ani mutum (kafiri). Mẽ yã yi kãfircinsa!","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:18","price":"Daga wane abu, (Allah) Ya halitta shi?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:19","price":"Daga ɗigon maniyyi, Ya halitta shi sa'an nan Ya ƙaddarã shi (ga halaye).","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:20","price":"Sa'an nan, hanyarsa ta fita Ya sauƙaƙe masa.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:21","price":"Sa'an nan, Ya matar da shi sai Ya sanya shi a cikin kabari.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:22","price":"Sa'an nan, idan Ya so lalle ne zai tãyar da shi.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:23","price":"Haƙĩƙa bai i da aikata abin da Allah Ya umurce shi ba (lõkacin sanya shi a cikin kabari).","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:24","price":"To, mutum ya dũba zuwa ga abincinsa.","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:25","price":"Lalle ne Mũ, Mun zuo ruwa, zubõwa.","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:26","price":"Sa'an nan, Muka tsattsãge ƙasa tsattsagewa.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:27","price":"Sa'an nan, Muka tsirar da ƙwaya, a cikinta.","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:28","price":"Da inabi da ciyãwa.","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:29","price":"Da zaitũni da itãcen dabĩno.","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:30","price":"Da lambuna, mãsu yawan itãce.","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:31","price":"Da 'yã'yan itãcen marmari, da makiyãyã ta dabbõbi.","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:32","price":"Domin jin dãɗi a gare ku, ku da dabbobinku.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:33","price":"To, idan mai tsãwa (busa ta biyu) ta zo.","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:34","price":"Rãnar da mutum yake gudu daga ɗan'uwansa.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:35","price":"Da uwarsa da ubansa.","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:36","price":"Da mãtarsa da ɗiyansa.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:37","price":"Ga kõwane mutum daga cikinsu, a rãnar nan akwai wani sha'ani da ya ishe shi.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:38","price":"Wasu huskõki, a rãnar nan, mãsu haske ne.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:39","price":"Mãsu dãriya ne, mãsu bushãra.","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:40","price":"Wasu huskõki, a rãnar nan, akwai ƙũra a kansu.","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:41","price":"Baƙi zai rufe su.","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"80:42","price":"Waɗannan sũ ne kãfirai fãjirai (ga ayyukansu).","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}